reviewText: Excellent.  See for yourself, what superb acting is all about.
Great deal! Dad cant wait to watch 'em all!

There are a number of true gems in this collection which make it worth owning, but the quality of some of the recordings is very poor and there are no subtitles to help you discern the dialog on the few with very scratchy audio.  Quality on others is much better though... and look how many films you're getting for the price. Any old movie buff will likely appreciate at least 20 of them.
Great if you love old movies which I do.
